iWhere was I? Oh right.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iStallman is in charge of GNU. This is good. Without someone in		gopher.black	70
icharge, GNU would float on the eddies of popular opinion. Instead,		gopher.black	70
iit is a bulwark standing for freedom. Freedom as in liberty.		gopher.black	70
iLiberty, which I've previously discussed, is diametrically opposed		gopher.black	70
ito equality. Of course that's how he runs things. Any other way		gopher.black	70
iwould be as ridiculous as the idea of censoring a joke about the		gopher.black	70
ioverreach of censorship in a project dedicated to fighting fucking		gopher.black	70
icensorship.		gopher.black	70
